        <marginalia hand="Italian">
            <language ident="EN">
                <position book_orientation="270" place="tail">
                    <marginalia_text>
                        The rarest men extend their vtterest possibilitie, with a fine (as it were) familiar sleight: &amp; they that do not enforce themselues to display their best, cum euer short, of their reckoning.
                    </marginalia_text>
                </position>
            </language>
        </marginalia>
        
        <marginalia hand="Italian">
            <language ident="EN">
                <position book_orientation="0" place="tail">
                    <marginalia_text>
                        { No excellent grace, or fine cumlie behauior without three cunning properties; a sound iudgment to informe;
                        an apt dexteritie to conforme; &amp; an earnest intention to performe.
                    </marginalia_text>
                </position>
            </language>
        </marginalia>
        
